Tube Atlas — Pixelle vendoring NOTICE
======================================

This subpackage (``core/pixelle/``) contains code and ideas adapted from
``Pixelle-Video`` by AIDC-AI (https://github.com/AIDC-AI/Pixelle-Video),
which is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

A copy of the Apache License is provided alongside this NOTICE in
``LICENSE-APACHE``.

Modifications:
- Adapted to plug into Tube Atlas's Streamlit pipeline
  (``Studio script → Producer mp4`` flow rather than Pixelle's own web UI).
- Trimmed to: TTS + ComfyUI client + LLM provider abstraction. Pixelle's
  full template / history / batch UI is not vendored.
- Default LLM provider is DeepSeek (existing in ``core/llm.py``); Google
  Gemini is supported as an optional fallback.
- Default TTS engine is Edge-TTS (no key required); IndexTTS / ChatTTS
  may be added in future revisions through the ``TTSAdapter`` interface.

